#: lib/tipping_web/components/layouts.ex:105
msgid "Beklager, nå surrer vi litt"
msgstr "Sorry, we’re having some issues"

#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:43
msgid "Bruk en bedriftskonto, så finner vi kollegaene dine :)"
msgstr "Use a work account so we can find your colleagues :)"

#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:106
msgid "Det er resultatet etter 90 minutter +&nbsp;tilleggstid som gjelder."
msgstr "The bet is for the result after 90 minutes +&nbsp;stoppage time."

#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:31
msgid "Du vet mer<br />om fotball enn<br />kollegaene dine"
msgstr "You know more<br />about football<br />than your<br />co-workers"

#: lib/tipping_web/components/layouts.ex:110
msgid "Et par sekunder bare, vi leter etter internett"
msgstr "Give us a minute, we’re trying to find the internet"

#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:24
msgid "Fotball-VM 2026"
msgstr "World Cup 2026"

#: lib/tipping_web/components/core_components.ex:375
msgid "Handlinger"
msgstr "Actions"

#: lib/tipping_web/components/layouts.ex:117
msgid "Hm, nå skjedde det noe"
msgstr "Hm, something happened"

#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:97
msgid "Konseptet er enkelt."
msgstr "The concept is simple."

#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:202
msgid "Korrekt målforskjell"
msgstr "Correct goal difference"

#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:198
msgid "Korrekt resultat"
msgstr "Correct result"

#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:206
msgid "Korrekt vinner"
msgstr "Correct winner"

#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:159
msgid "Laget i Sogndal av"
msgstr "Made in Sogndal by"

#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:124
msgid "Litt om personvern og sånn"
msgstr "Regarding privacy"

#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:37
#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:40
msgid "Logg inn med %{provider}"
msgstr "Log in with %{provider}"

#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:99
msgid ""
"Logg inn med en bedriftskonto, tipp hva resultatet kommer til å bli i VM-kampene,\n"
"        og vinn heder og ære."
msgstr "Log in with a work account, bet on the World Cup results, win eternal glory."

#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:111
msgid "Poeng beregnes som følger:"
msgstr "Points are calculated as follows:"

#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:109
msgid "Siste frist for å tippe på en kamp er 10 minutter før avspark."
msgstr "Last call to make a bet is 10 minutes before kickoff."

#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:141
msgid "Tilbakemeldinger, spørsmål, ris, ros, varme tanker og blomster kan sendes til <code>post@eaj.no</code>."
msgstr "Feedback, questions, complaints, praise, thoughts&nbsp;&&nbsp;prayers and flowers can be sent to <code>post@eaj.no</code>."

#: lib/tipping_web/components/layouts.ex:122
msgid "Vi forsøker å fikse det"
msgstr "We’re trying to fix things"

#: lib/tipping_web/components/core_components.ex:81
msgid "lukk"
msgstr "close"

#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:114
msgid ""
"Å delta er gratis. Premie er som nevnt heder og ære. Eventuelt\n"
"        muligheten til å skryte en liten stund. Det får dere avklare internt,\n"
"        tenker jeg."
msgstr "Participation is free. The main prize is, as mentioned, eternal glory. And maybe bragging rights for a while. I’ll leave that up to you."

#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:127
msgid ""
"Når du logger inn lagrer vi en unik identfikator som vi får fra Google/Microsoft,\n"
"      navnet ditt, og domenet til e-posten din (det etter <code>@</code>-tegnet).\n"
"      Dette er de tre tingene siden trenger for å fungere, så mer enn det tar\n"
"      vi ikke vare på."
msgstr "When you log in we store a unique identifier we get from Google/Microsoft, your name, and the domain of your email (the part after the <code>@</code>-sign). This is all we need in order for the site to work, so we don’t keep anything else."

#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:33
msgid "Nå gjenstår det bare å bevise det."
msgstr "Now you’ve just got to prove it."

#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:103
msgid "Regler"
msgstr "Rules"

#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:138
msgid "Noe du vil melde?"
msgstr "Any thoughts?"

#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:74
msgid "Deg?"
msgstr "You?"

#: lib/tipping_web/components/home_components.ex:61
msgid "Kolleagen din?"
msgstr "Your colleague?"
